B.Se=s(["Long ago, the Chaos Nation was protected by the ancient power of the Oliverson Realm, a magical land where memes, madness, and survival energy became real.","When the Glitch Chaos Gates opened, ridiculous enemies from every dimension began invading the realm. The Oliverson Realm could not answer with kings, knights, or armies. Instead, it summoned ordinary outsiders whose chaotic energy was strong enough to become legendary.","Kurt, Kevin, Myrna, Theo, and Whitey now stand together as the Chosen Defenders. They must cross five corrupted lands, protect every base, and close the gates before chaos consumes the nation permanently."],t.s)
B.Vu=new A.nb("The Chaos Nation","The Glitch Chaos Gates are open","ui/boot/main_menu_backdrop_v1.png",B.Se)
B.SO=s(["Before he became a hero, Kurt was a playful kid enjoying a game of tumbang preso with his friends. His weapon was simple: one old but surprisingly powerful tsinelas.","During one perfect throw, the slipper struck the can so hard that it opened a glowing crack in reality. Before Kurt could retrieve it, the portal swallowed him and pulled him into the Oliverson Realm.","The ancient spirits recognized his accuracy, courage, and unstoppable Filipino slipper energy. His humble tsinelas transformed into the Legendary Slipper of Judgment.","Now Kurt defends the Chaos Nation at close range, striking enemies with magical slippers that stun, knock back, and embarrass anything foolish enough to invade his road."],t.s)
B.Vt=new A.nb("Kurt the Tsinelas Champion","Bearer of the Legendary Slipper of Judgment",u.L,B.SO)
B.RH=s(["Kevin was feared in every comment section. He typed faster than anyone, argued with strangers for hours, and never backed down from an online fight.","During one massive argument, his keyboard began glowing with chaotic purple light. Every angry word he typed became real. His screen cracked open and dragged him into the Oliverson Realm.","Chaos energy transformed his keyboard into a weapon, his comments into projectiles, and his rage into fuel. He now fires BRUH, LOL, GG, NO, and RATIO like bullets.","Deep inside Kevin waits the chaotic form of everything he once was. When pushed too far, he becomes the Caps Lock Berserker."],t.s)
B.Vw=new A.nb("Kevin the Keyboard Warrior","The Caps Lock Berserker",u.A,B.RH)
B.TK=s(["Myrna was the undefeated queen of every family karaoke night. No birthday, reunion, fiesta, or neighborhood gathering was complete without her holding the microphone.","One night, her final note became so powerful that the speaker exploded, the lights flickered, and a portal opened behind the karaoke machine. Myrna did not stop singing. The portal carried her voice into the Oliverson Realm.","The realm chose her because her voice could shake monsters, inspire allies, and force enemies to dance against their will.","Myrna now wields her microphone as a magical weapon. Her songs create shockwaves, stun invaders, and turn every battlefield into a chaotic concert."],t.s)
B.Vv=new A.nb("Myrna the Karaoke Auntie","The Unrelenting Voice of the Realm",u.r,B.TK)
B.TI=s(["Theo was a quiet technician trying to fix everyone's internet. Every day brought the same questions: Why is it lagging? Who changed the password? Why is there no signal?","One stormy night, while restarting a router for the hundredth time, lightning struck the antenna. The router flashed with impossible blue light and its WiFi signal formed a magic circle around him.","Theo arrived in a realm where weak signals, lag spikes, and broken connections had become real monsters. The realm gave him a staff made from an ancient router, and he became the WiFi Wizard.","He controls lag, signal waves, buffering zones, and connection storms. Enemies caught in his magic crawl as though trapped at 999ms ping."],t.s)
B.Vs=new A.nb("Theo the WiFi Wizard","Keeper of the Ancient Router",u.N,B.TI)
B.Rk=s(["Whitey was never an ordinary dog. Behind his innocent face and loyal heart lived an ancient golden energy connected to luck, courage, and protection.","One night, Whitey saw a glowing portal open beneath the moon. From it came the cries of the Oliverson Realm. With one brave bark, he jumped through without hesitation.","The ancient spirits recognized Whitey as a pure-hearted guardian. His loyalty could protect the weak, and his courage was bright enough to challenge the darkness.","The sacred Whitey Coin awakened within him. Forged from loyalty, luck, and guardian energy, it bounces between enemies, deals sacred damage, confuses chaos monsters, and rewards the defenders with bonus coins."],t.s)
B.Vr=new A.nb("Whitey","Guardian of the Sacred Whitey Coin",u.Z,B.Rk)
B.rO=s([B.Vu,B.Vt,B.Vw,B.Vv,B.Vs,B.Vr],A.a7("D<nb>"))
